Description: ikunfrailty stands for Imputation of covariates for
    Kinship-induced Unobserved frailty under Nonrandom ascertainment. This
    research package implements the proposed posterior-draw multiple
    imputation method for the frailtypack ascertainment-corrected correlated
    frailty model targeted by the V2.2 technical note. The validated first
    engine supports one continuous polygenic risk score covariate and one
    binary carrier covariate, separately or jointly missing, and exposes
    pooled parameter estimates and penetrance summaries.
